          <p>Choir was my heartbeat: honors choir, swing choir, the Dorian Vocal Festival. I went on to win both the <em>National School Choral Award</em> and the <em>John Philip Sousa Award</em> ‚Äî the top honors in band and choir ‚Äî sweeping them as one determined girl.</p>
          <div class="quote">‚ÄúI grew up stifled by perfection and rules that changed on a whim ‚Äî but the wonder was always there, waiting.‚Äù</div>
