          <p>I became <strong>InformationMommy</strong>, sharing fact-based, sassy, no-nonsense videos on everything from cloth diapering to vaccine research to day-in-the-life chaos. Over 1,000 subscribers later, I had built a little community that turned into real friendships ‚Äî women I met up with, confided in, and leaned on.</p>
          <p>That community showed me the power of connection: finding people who are walking through the same season as you. It was also the first time I started uncovering <em>me</em> ‚Äî not just the daughter of a narcissist, not just a wife or mom, not just an employee, but Parker.</p>
